term.name: House Committee on Science, Space, and Technology

bill.summary: This resolution elects designated Members of the House of Representatives to the Committee on Agriculture; the Committee on Armed Services; the Committee on Foreign Affairs; the Committee on Science, Space, and Technology; and the Committee on the Budget.
